text: heliri; allahane ella vastugala odeyanagiruvaga nanenu allahana horatu berobba devarannu hudukabeke? Pratiyobbanu tanu sampadisiruvudakkella tane honegaranagiruttane. Hore horuva yarobbaru innobbara horeyannu horalararu. Antimavagi nivu nim'ma odeyana kadege maralabekagide. Nivu bhinnate talidda ella visayagala vastavavannu avanu nimage tilisuvanu
